Today Qin Ke and Zhuo Hao

153
00:09:48,199 --> 00:09:49,240
were so gullible that

154
00:09:49,759 --> 00:09:51,160
they spoke for Demon Zi.

155
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:53,399
